Zabryna Guevara https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zabryna_Guevara 0 Zabryna Guevara (born January 12, 1972) is an American actress. She is known for playing the role of Melania Ortiz in 3 lbs and Sarah Essen in Gotham. Guevara is also a theatrical actress and in 2013 held the role of Yazmin in the award-winning Quiara Alegría Hudes play Water by the Spoonful at Second Stage Theater. She is of mixed Hispanic and black descent. Zabryna_Guevara ( born January_12_,_1972 ) is an_American_actress . She is_known for playing the_role of Melania_Ortiz in 3_lbs and Sarah_Essen in Gotham .
